WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.800
If you've got a Bible with you, please turn with me to Romans chapter 15.

2
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:09.040
It's also there in your worship guide if you need that.

3
00:00:09.040 --> 00:00:14.000
In Romans chapter 15 verse 6, we're told that the church has been brought together that

4
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:19.040
we might glorify God with one voice.

5
00:00:19.040 --> 00:00:23.240
And over the past couple of weeks, we've been looking at this kind of short series,

6
00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:27.800
just looking at Romans 15 and seeing what it means for us to come together to glorify

7
00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:29.160
God with one voice.

8
00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:32.600
You saw, first of all, we glorify Him with our worship.

9
00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:36.760
That includes singing praises to God as we've just done, but it's so much more than that

10
00:00:36.760 --> 00:00:37.760
as well.

11
00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:44.440
It's ultimately humbling our lives, ourselves before the Lord that He might be exalted.

12
00:00:44.440 --> 00:00:49.080
Everything we do should be out of a heart of worship to the Lord because of His great

13
00:00:49.080 --> 00:00:51.280
