14
00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:55.160
But also, we are to glorify God through our welcome.

15
00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:58.920
So we're to welcome one another within the life of the church as we have been welcomed

16
00:00:58.920 --> 00:01:00.160
by Jesus.

17
00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:06.840
And as we welcome one another, we begin to grow together in the likeness of Christ.

18
00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:10.480
And then lastly, which is where we're at today, we see that we are going to glorify

19
00:01:10.480 --> 00:01:12.800
God through our witness.

20
00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:14.360
That's what we're called to as well.

21
00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:19.160
So we don't just want to glorify God behind closed doors in the life of the church.

22
00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:24.480
We want His glory to shine out from here throughout North Jefferson and the communities

23
00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:28.480
we're part of and on to the ends of the earth.

24
00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:37.600
So Romans chapter 15, this morning we're going to read verses 14 down to the end of the chapter.

25
00:01:37.600 --> 00:01:43.440
It says, I myself am satisfied about you, my brothers, that you yourselves are full of

26
00:01:43.440 --> 00:01:48.960
goodness filled with all knowledge and able to instruct one another.

27
00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:54.440
But on some points I have written to you very boldly by way of reminder because of

28
00:01:54.440 --> 00:01:57.160
the grace given to me by God.

29
00:01:57.160 --> 00:02:03.520
To be a minister of Christ Jesus to the Gentiles in the priestly service of the Gospel of God.

30
00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:09.760
So that the offering of the Gentiles may be acceptable, sanctified by the Holy Spirit.

31
00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:13.960
In Christ Jesus then I have reason to be proud of my work for God.

32
00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:17.760
For I will not venture to speak of anything except what Christ has accomplished through

33
00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:23.360
me to bring the Gentiles to obedience by word and deed.

34
00:02:23.360 --> 00:02:26.160
By the power of signs and wonders.

35
00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:28.600
By the power of the Spirit of God.

36
00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:33.720
So that from Jerusalem and all the way around to Illyricum I have fulfilled the ministry

37
00:02:33.720 --> 00:02:35.800
of the Gospel of Christ.

38
00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:39.800
And thus I make it my ambition to preach the Gospel not where Christ has already been

39
00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:43.680
named lest I build on someone else's foundation.

40
00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:48.800
But as it is written, those who have never been told of Him will see and those who

41
00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:51.360
have never heard will understand.

42
00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:55.680
This is the reason why I have so often been hindered from coming to you.

43
00:02:55.680 --> 00:03:00.800
But now since I no longer have any room to work in these regions and since I have longed

44
00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:05.960
for many years to come to you, I hope to see you in passing as I go to Spain and be helped

45
00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:08.360
on my journey there by you.

46
00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:11.400
Once I have enjoyed your company for a while.

47
00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:15.920
At present however I am going to Jerusalem bringing aid to the saints.

48
00:03:15.920 --> 00:03:20.480
For Macedonia and Achaia have been pleased to make some contribution for the poor among

49
00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.280
the saints at Jerusalem.

50
00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:26.480
For they were pleased to do it and indeed they owe it to them for if the Gentiles have

51
00:03:26.480 --> 00:03:31.320
come to share in their spiritual blessings they ought also to be of service to them in

52
00:03:31.320 --> 00:03:33.560
material blessings.

53
00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:38.920
When therefore I have completed this and have delivered to them what has been collected,

54
00:03:38.920 --> 00:03:41.960
I will leave for Spain by way of you.

55
00:03:41.960 --> 00:03:46.160
I know that when I come to you I will come in the fullness of the blessing of

56
00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:47.440
Christ.

57
00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:53.080
I appeal to you brothers by our Lord Jesus Christ and by the love of the Spirit to strive

58
00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:58.120
together with me in your prayers to God on my behalf that I may be delivered from the

59
00:03:58.120 --> 00:04:00.320
unbelievers in Judea.

60
00:04:00.320 --> 00:04:06.400
That my service for Jerusalem may be acceptable to the saints so that by God's will I

61
00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:10.520
may come to you with joy and be refreshed in your company.

62
00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:12.720
May the God of peace be with you all.

63
00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:13.720
Amen.

64
00:04:13.720 --> 00:04:15.720
This is the word of the Lord.

65
00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:17.720
Let's pray.

66
00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:22.440
Lord as we come now to your word I pray that you would open our eyes that we might be

67
00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:24.200
hold wondrous things there.

68
00:04:24.200 --> 00:04:28.200
I pray that your spirit would open the eyes of our hearts that we might be hold more

69
00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:29.480
of the glory of Jesus.

70
00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:33.160
Lord I pray that we would be drawn to him and that we would be changed into his

71
00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:34.160
likeness.

72
00:04:34.160 --> 00:04:35.600
We pray this in his name.

73
00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:36.600
Amen.

74
00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:45.160
Well during a visit to the NASA Space Center back in 1962 President John F. Kennedy

75
00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:48.040
noticed a janitor who was there.

76
00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:52.560
He was pushing his broom and he interrupted the tour and kind of walked over to the man

77
00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:54.040
and said he introduced himself.

78
00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:55.480
He said, hi I'm Jack Kennedy.

79
00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:57.080
What are you doing there?

80
00:04:57.080 --> 00:05:03.040
And the janitor replied, well Mr. President I'm helping to put a man on the moon.

81
00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:05.080
So this man had a specific job.

82
00:05:05.080 --> 00:05:09.520
He was the janitor but he saw what he was doing in light of the greater

83
00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:14.680
mission that he was part of.

