00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:23.040
called to and yet we have a greater mission that we are all part of.

86
00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:29.080
We are all called to make God's glory known yes here but also to the ends of

87
00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:30.440
the earth.

