00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:11.480
So yes we are among those nations that have been shown mercy in Christ but also

98
00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:16.600
participants in the mission of God to make that gospel, the gospel of Jesus known

99
00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:19.000
throughout the world.

100
00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:21.480
And so that's what we're going to be seeing this morning.

