00:07:10.200 --> 00:07:13.720
He's writing to every believer, every member of the church.

118
00:07:13.720 --> 00:07:20.400
You see God wants you to know what his word teaches about global mission.

119
00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:22.920
If you've got your Bible with you and you can look at that previous

120
00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:25.960
section that we were reading over the past couple of weeks where you have

